OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774285870
OL,3,C34 sheep dead after dog attack
OL,5,FThirty-four sheep have died after a
OL,6,Fdog attack on a farm in Lincolnshire.
OL,8,FThe ewes, which were all pregnant,
OL,9,Fwere in a field off Haugham Road, near
OL,10,FTathwell, south of Louth, when the
OL,11,Fincident happened in the early hours
OL,12,Fof 13 February.
OL,14,FLincolnshire Police said four were
OL,15,Fkilled at the scene.
OL,17,FThe others died from their injuries or
OL,18,Ffrom shock.
OL,20,FOfficers said the farmer suffered
OL,21,F#15,000 in losses.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
