OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774285870
OL,3,C34 sheep dead after dog attack
OL,5,FDet Con Aaron Flint said: "Incidents
OL,6,Flike this are devastating for farmers,
OL,7,Fboth emotionally and financially.
OL,9,F"Livestock worrying is a serious
OL,10,Foffence, and dog owners must take
OL,11,Fresponsibility for ensuring their
OL,12,Fanimals are properly controlled at all
OL,13,Ftimes.
OL,15,F"Even a normally well-behaved dog can
OL,16,Finstinctively chase or attack
OL,17,Flivestock if given the opportunity."
OL,19,FAfter a change in the law anyone
OL,20,Fresponsible for allowing a dog to
OL,21,Fattack sheep can face unlimited fines.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
